    "title": "Junior SEO Specialist at Noise",
    "description": "Grow your career with Noise! We are hiring a SEO Specialist for our Ranchi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Noise:\nNoise is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Noise!",
